title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 28 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 - Dec 28 2021
description:
EIB Guest Host Michael Berry, from NewsRadio 740 KTRH in Houston, rolls his interview with President Trump on the 2020 election, McConnell's weakness, and his golf game. Whistleblower pilot from Airline Employees 4 Health Freedom calls with blockbuster: They didn’t have to cancel all those flights. Biden promised to shut down the virus, but now he throws up his hands saying there's "not a federal solution."
